⏱️ AI Time Management System

An intelligent AI-powered time management system designed to help users optimize their daily schedules, set smart reminders, and increase productivity. This project leverages AI algorithms to analyze user habits, predict time usage, and provide personalized recommendations for better efficiency.

🚀 Features

🧠 AI-driven Task Scheduling – Automatically prioritizes tasks based on deadlines, importance, and estimated effort.

⏰ Smart Reminders – Sends adaptive reminders that adjust based on progress and user behavior.

📊 Productivity Insights – Generates detailed analytics on time spent and suggests improvements.

🔄 Habit Learning – Learns user routines and suggests optimized schedules.

🌐 Cross-Platform Support – Works on desktop and mobile environments.

💾 Data Persistence – Securely stores and manages task history and preferences.

🛠️ Tech Stack


AI/ML Models: scikit-learn, TensorFlow, or PyTorch (depending on your implementation)

Other Tools: Pandas, NumPy, REST API integration

⚙️ Installation & Setup

Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ai-time-management-system.git
cd ai-time-management-system


Create Virtual Environment

python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate   # Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate      # Windows


Install Dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt


Run Backend Server

python backend/app.py


Run Frontend (if React/Flutter)

cd frontend
npm install
npm start

🧪 Usage

Add tasks with deadlines, importance, and estimated duration.

The AI engine suggests an optimized daily/weekly plan.

Track progress and receive adaptive reminders.

View productivity analytics via dashboard.

📊 Example Workflow

User inputs tasks → "Finish Report" (High Priority, 3 hrs, Due Tomorrow).

AI assigns optimal time slots considering user’s past focus hours.

Reminder adapts if user misses planned time.

Dashboard updates with time spent and productivity score.

🤖 Future Enhancements

Integration with Google Calendar / Outlook

Voice-based AI assistant for task management

Reinforcement learning for better habit adaptation

Mobile app with push notifications

